  %p= "We collect the information which you fill in on our site. This includes registration, commenting on posts and using our chat function."

  %p= "Note: We strive to create a global community with consistent standards for everyone, but we also try to respect local laws. The following provision applies to users outside the United States: You consent to having your personal data transferred to and processed in the United States."

