  %p= "This online privacy policy applies only to information collected through our website and not to information collected offline."
  %h5= "Terms and Conditions"
  %p= "Please visit our Terms and Conditions section establishing the use, disclaimers, and limitations of liability governing the use of our website here: Terms and Conditions"
